  "text": "English word embedding was obtained from Word2vec-api 3 . The embedding dimension is 100 and it was trained using GloVe with AdaGrad. For the generation of Spanish word embeddings we followed [CITATION_1] , using Spanish Gigaword Third Edition 4 as corpus with an embedding dimension of 64, a minimum word frequency cutoff of 4 and a window size of 8.",
